dc_title_s: Pierhead and bulkhead lines for Raritan River, New Jersey, from Crab Island to the head of Navigation New Brunswick
dc_description_s: Pierhead and bulkhead lines for Raritan River, New Jersey, from Crab Island to the head of Navigation New Brunswick, as recomended by the New York Harbor Line Board, appointed for the establishment of the harbor lines of New York Harbor and its adjacent waters by Special Order No. 49.
